When it was uploaded to YouTube on December 3, 2018, WWE blocked it because of the TD. However, on December 6, for a short time, the video was unblocked and then it got blocked AGAIN. Finally, on December 9, it got unblocked again...and then, Jordan Rios deleted all of the LSNs on his account, including this. Luckily, I got em' saved in time!

metadata.description: On January 13th, 2018, a false alarm Emergency Alert System message was sent out for the entire state of Hawaii warning of a impending nuclear missile attack. This particular Civil Defense warning interrupted a CBS college basketball game between Ole Miss and Florida. This was most likely broadcasted on KGMB and was clarified as a error a few minutes later.
